title: Findel-Hawkins, Zuern Finish Play at Saint Francis Health System ITA All-American Championships
text: advanced past the Qualifying Doubles Round of 32, but saw their time end at the Saint Francis Health System ITA All-American Championships end in the Round of 16. Findel-Hawkins and Zuern, who were seeded No. 9-16 in Qualifying Doubles, started the day by edging out TCU's Hudson Blake and Trevor Johnson 7-6 (7), 6-4 in the Round of 32. However, the duo fell to No. 2 Qualifying Doubles seeded Hayden Sabatka and Bart Van Leijsen of New Mexico 7-5, 6-2. UNF men's tennis returns to action at the four-day ITA Regionals Tournament that is being held at Florida's Alfred A. Ring Tennis Complex Oct. 15-18 in Gainesville.
